com.versant.var.common
Class VARGlobals

java.lang.Object
  com.versant.var.common.VARGlobals

public class VARGlobals
extends java.lang.Object

This class keeps references to all the global objects. All the members are static references. Its Initialize() method should be called after the configuration file has been read.
